{"tid":1524071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人私了？","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:43:33.000Z","uid":49967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f050c3faaa7dc4f758eb402836fa827fa207e04","tid":1524071,"uid":49967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"點解今時今日我哋一味比狗欺壓都唔肯去反擊？<br />\n因為我哋私了要付出代價而班狗無囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想劏狗就一定要自動波開遮掩護私了嘅勇武<br />\n好似班狗咁做，唔比其他人知道自己身份，咁落手就會乾脆好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要令所有人都有殺狗嘅共識，而唔係比自己嘅罪惡感，道德鉫鎖束縛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋無得唔還擊架啦，要贏就要做少少污糟嘅手段。"},{"pid":"d848d59781bb3ddbf54ab6803b3ff9295ea8fe26","tid":1524071,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"唔好咁做呀，咁做好撚大鑊，推到老豆搵仔admin見到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88933efa972944522f1f05ec96a4f7616f906d19","tid":1524071,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試下找不同？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15481babae8b13bfed8369d13faacd742e934a34","tid":1524071,"uid":49967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"最重要係大家一定要有個意識<br />\n私了嘅時候自動波開遮比勇武<br />\n無人幫就唔洗旨意有人去做。"}]}